skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: health tips
des:
Every time you ask it for a health tip, it will tell you one from its database. There are tens of the best health tips around. We made sure they're easy to follow and provide lots of value.
Note that these tips do NOT replace a doctor's visit. They're just for informative purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
